text: 1330 was a year in the Julian calendar starting on a Monday. It was the 30th year of the 14th century. ==Births== *June 15 - Edward, the Black Prince, first Prince of Wales and first son of King Edward III of England (died 1376) *date unknown **John Wycliffe, English scholar (died 1382) **William V of Holland, Count of Holland, Dutch nobleman ==Deaths== *Roger de Mortimer, 1st Earl of March, English nobleman and politician (born 1287) Category:1330
